          "name": "t:names.text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At The Pink Cottage, we want you to love your purchase. If something isn’t quite right, we’re happy to help with an easy return or exchange.</p><h3>Returns & Exchanges</h3><ul><li>Items may be returned within 30 days of delivery</li><li>Returns are accepted for any reason, provided items are unworn, unwashed, and in original condition with tags attached</li></ul><h3>How to Start a Return</h3><p>To initiate a return or exchange, please visit our <a href=\"https://lillyspinkcottage.com/apps/redo/returns-portal\" target=\"_blank\">returns portal</a> and follow the steps provided. Once your return is approved, securely package the item and send it back according to the instructions provided.</p><h3>Shipping & Processing</h3><ul><li>Return shipping costs are the responsibility of the customer unless the item is defective or sent in error</li><li>We recommend using a trackable shipping method</li><li>Once received and inspected, refunds are processed within 3–5 business days and issued to the original form of payment</li></ul><h3>Final Sale & Non-Returnable Items</h3><p>The following items are final sale and not eligible for return or refund:</p><ul><li>Sale items</li><li>Items purchased using a coupon or promotional code</li><li>Items marked “Final Sale” on the product page</li><li>Items purchased during promotional events that are clearly stated as final sale</li></ul><p>Certain items may also be non-returnable for hygiene or customization reasons. These will be clearly noted on the product page.All Kendra Scott and any other jewelry.</p><h3>Gift With Purchase (GWP)</h3><p>For orders that include a <strong>Gift With Purchase</strong>, the GWP must be returned if requesting a full refund. If the GWP is not returned, the refund amount will be reduced by the retail value of the GWP.</p><h3>Questions?</h3><p>If you have any questions about returns or exchanges, please contact our customer service team — we’re always happy to help.</p>",
